{"tid":396451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"操普通話教大生民主牆貼標語　促嚴懲惡徒","createTime":"2017-09-11T16:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T03:33:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1754046ccfa1d10315e8689ec2be5f0084a8ddc7","tid":396451,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"香港教育大學民主牆先後有人張貼奚落教育局副局長蔡若蓮喪子標語，以及冒犯劉曉波夫婦的字句。一群操普通話、自稱是教育大學的學生，今午(11日)到民主牆張貼標語字句「支持學校徹查追責」及「還我教大清譽」。<br />\n<br />\n約10名學生早上11時在教大中央廣場不斷高叫口號：「嚴懲冷血惡徒。」他們指，反對學生會包庇惡徒，支持學校徹查及追究責任，並須予以嚴懲。他們又在場派發傳單及呼籲拒絕被學生會代表的學生聯署簽名支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170911/photo/bkn-20170911131318984-0911_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170911140536\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170911%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170911131318984-0911_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170911140536&h=539be452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170911/photo/bkn-20170911131318984-0911_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170911140536\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170911%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170911131318984-0911_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170911140536&h=e76118df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c3bf0f512f6327ae4e8a1854645e1779935419c","tid":396451,"uid":30966,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"靚助攻"},{"pid":"eea7760ef127d91adc56b1414f82638220b477ad","tid":396451,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x78vcaqd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx78vcaqd&h=ccfef170&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca6818c7f51ee4ee5e6169e493b40ed9425e2c97","tid":396451,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea334d5cf63e12f6b346